  "detailed_description": "Puzzlement is a minimal puzzle game based on walking/jumping between plane surfaces. The goal is simple; collect all red squares.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/775530/extras/5b201834bc967ac253cb26f13199fe82.poster.avif?t=1556396159\" width=666 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/775530/extras/5b201834bc967ac253cb26f13199fe82.webm?t=1556396159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/775530/extras/5b201834bc967ac253cb26f13199fe82.mp4?t=1556396159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 beautifully crafted mind bending levels</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing music & sounds</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100% indie - designed and developed by two people</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>keyboard - to walk & jump & climb</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>mouse - to rotate</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundtrack (by Ozan Barış)</h2>Spotify: <br><br>Youtube:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achievements</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/775530/extras/2662985ba81bbb648dcd6ba59e052a1a.avif?t=1556396159\" width=500 height=100 /></span>",
